T1  - Endogenous Borrowing Constraints With Incomplete Markets
AU  - ZHANG, HAROLD H.
Y1  - 1997/12/01
PY  - 1997
DA  - 1997/12/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1540-6261.1997.tb02758.x
